title: Ore no Imouto ga Konna ni Kawaii Wake ga Nai - LOVE REPLICA (Doujinshi)
description:
Kirino's A/C is out of order, so she goes to play eroge at Kyosuke's room.
With the game's sfx, Kyosuke's pent-up frustration and Kirino's tempting attire, what will happen to Kyosuke's self control?

And will Kirino even try to resist the things to come?
